  <name>TomodOrange</name>
  <summary>Native COSMIC™ Pomodoro timer for deep focus</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      TomodOrange is a lightweight, native Pomodoro timer designed specifically for the COSMIC™ desktop.
      It prioritizes a distraction-free environment with rhythmic audio cues and high-contrast visuals.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Native libcosmic performance</li>
      <li>Always-on-top floating timer</li>
      <li>Mokugyo rhythmic ticking for flow state</li>
      <li>Zero-distraction minutes-only display</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
